Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:46.35,Main,split,0,0,0,,{It is... It is...}Phải rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{I got it!}Phải rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:52.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{Dogs are better than horses after all!}Chó đúng là tốt hơn ngựa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{Most things get better if I kick 'em.}Thường thì đá như vậy có hiệu quả.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:02.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{You just don't know when to quit.}Chỉ là cậu không biết khi nào phải dừng.
