Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{Huh? [added this}Hể?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, helllllloooooo...}Này, có ai ở đó không?
