Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.17,Main,split,0,0,0,,{What was the treasure we were after?}Kho báu chúng ta theo đuổi là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:56.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{The Tamatebako, was it?}Tamatebako, nhớ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:02.08,Main,split,0,0,0,,{I kinda see why the man\Nturned into an old geezer}Giờ tôi mới hiểu tại sao\N chàng trai lại biến thành ông lão {after opening the Tamatebako now.}sau khi mở nó ra.
Comment: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:59.69,Main,split,0,0,0,,{I kinda see why the man\Nturned into an old geezer}Giờ tôi mới hiểu tại sao\N chàng trai lại biến thành ông lão
